This paper is about a framework for distributed model selection and training, which is a common problem in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Additionally, the paper mentions hyperparameter search algorithms, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV) applications.
